~ start_cow_pasture_box
do change_emote_visibility.emit(false)
Pasture box: The animals are hungry.
Pasture box: Do you want to feed your cows?
- Yes, feed them
	if food_storage > 0:
		do GameDialogueManager.feed_the_animals.emit()
	else:
		Pasture box: You don't have enough food
- No, they seem will fed
do animated_sprite.play("chest_close")
do interactable_label_component.show()
=> END


